alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Before Kitsch became a global beauty favorite, it was just Cassandra and a big idea. Meet our founder and get a glimpse into her world and discover the Kitsch products she can’t live without.</span></p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="4d11e11e-f2da-4d12-ab0c-55880015f1f5" class="r-1nwfr63"><picture data-rid="9b2ef1a6-482f-4784-9d4f-efe13a47f62a" class="r-p1r86n"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/8dd11e95-d9d6-408b-ab7a-bf060b12f0de?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/8dd11e95-d9d6-408b-ab7a-bf060b12f0de?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/8dd11e95-d9d6-408b-ab7a-bf060b12f0de?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/8dd11e95-d9d6-408b-ab7a-bf060b12f0de" class="r-sxbx17" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="4beacc99-7167-47a4-a499-b7e38a04ea1a" class="r-1eih1ba"><div data-rid="de1c1a67-6992-45a8-9a35-90c37469cd16" class="r-qe6ttv alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-62756da6-cf96-41b8-9068-07a5127bb6f6-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-e5ab0755-192d-43fb-99db-0f3b62468fef-attributes-textdecoration:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><p><span>Cassandra Thurswell</span></p><p></p></span></div><div data-rid="824c3a6f-7b84-445b-9309-690d58791b97" class="r-ohpnjc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong><span>Founder & CEO</span></strong></p></span></div><div data-rid="93b9600d-451a-49ff-a456-e437d30b1fb4" class="r-ux8mjb alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-d3101180-26d7-4941-8157-f0b0de59b8ca-attributes-textdecoration:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Cassandra launched Kitsch in 2010 with a clear mission: create high-quality beauty essentials that are practical, elevated, and accessible to all. With no outside funding, she built the brand from the ground up—driven by instinct, creativity, and a deep understanding of what modern beauty consumers actually want.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">From hair ties to heatless curls, Cassandra’s product ideas are rooted in solving real-life beauty challenges. She’s not afraid to go against the grain, reinventing everyday routines through innovation, sustainability, and a strong sense of style.</span></p><br><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">As a founder, she remains deeply involved in every part of the brand—from product development to customer experience—ensuring Kitsch always stays true to its vision: thoughtful products that make you feel good, look good, and do good.</span></p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="82c30cbb-8952-4943-b956-c4302c4a1ff5" class="r-8a1a2u"><div data-rid="f3bd53a6-7ee2-4f67-865a-14abb6e110ea" class="r-1mxjecf"><div data-rid="ba8b744b-363c-42b6-827a-004642fe1730" class="r-19d0kdd"><picture data-rid="e251752e-df90-4c57-9336-d807338fa976" class="r-1uey7vd"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/10563105-dd2c-4774-8cbe-ba9457a81e8d?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/10563105-dd2c-4774-8cbe-ba9457a81e8d?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/10563105-dd2c-4774-8cbe-ba9457a81e8d?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/10563105-dd2c-4774-8cbe-ba9457a81e8d" class="r-12cn7z5" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="98b42d72-4f8a-411b-85ce-629bab704b97" class="r-1nfyxpm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Cassandra Thurswell on The Power of Micro-Intentions</p></span></div><div data-rid="6e23d8c8-f1a8-4e22-97fc-7724116e766a" class="r-13nr17j alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-d3101180-26d7-4941-8157-f0b0de59b8ca-attributes-textdecoration:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><p>Gwyneth Paltrow sits down with Cassandra Thurswell, founder and CEO of Kitsch, to explore how seven failed ventures, a few handmade hair ties, and a one-paragraph plan sparked a global beauty empire. Thurswell opens up about bootstrapping realities, creating viral products, and staying grounded in Kitsch’s mission of accessibility, sustainability, and innovation.</p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/cassandra-thurswell-on-the-power-of-micro-intentions/id1352546554"><u>click here to listen</u></a></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="766e1e52-b8e9-4c96-ace3-262ab4261f39" class="r-39o1o3"><picture data-rid="c4f9828a-b748-4ea9-ac3e-8ac4c151a2b0" class="r-157x61z"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/a04cb038-c2f1-4670-9e7c-8dbf4b6261e0?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/a04cb038-c2f1-4670-9e7c-8dbf4b6261e0?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/a04cb038-c2f1-4670-9e7c-8dbf4b6261e0?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/a04cb038-c2f1-4670-9e7c-8dbf4b6261e0" alt="Two hair product boxes with pink ribbons on a pink background." class="r-uvltg8" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="ed81c3dd-5d60-48c7-bf14-6fb4b880fa0e" class="r-1kipaw2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Cassandra Thurswell on The Art of Incrementality</p></span></div><div data-rid="dd37403b-2ad0-46b8-ace1-bfed7138afa8" class="r-sg6agr alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-d3101180-26d7-4941-8157-f0b0de59b8ca-attributes-textdecoration:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hNM8OfcLOrI"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Despite uncertain times — tariffs, market fluctuations, and industry complexities — we remain committed to what works:&nbsp;incrementality, diversification and meeting the customer where they are.</span></a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hNM8OfcLOrI"><u>watch here</u></a></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="acd47f15-af81-43bc-8026-ea636dd05456" class="r-1yqsur1"><picture data-rid="099f929a-5af0-4a3c-b36c-7073bd86d13f" class="r-1h9ggwh"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/06c761c5-5986-4a51-964c-88936a059fcd?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/06c761c5-5986-4a51-964c-88936a059fcd?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/06c761c5-5986-4a51-964c-88936a059fcd?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/06c761c5-5986-4a51-964c-88936a059fcd" class="r-1dl5jwd" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="842d04d7-624a-4e66-86ec-86e8f391b630" class="r-4xv5hu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h1><span>Bootstrapped and Booming with Kitsch’s Cassandra Morales Thurswell</span></h1></span></div><div data-rid="b6867512-815a-4b3c-a010-52304e5ef2ec" class="r-158iozc alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-d3101180-26d7-4941-8157-f0b0de59b8ca-attributes-textdecoration:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><p>On today’s episode, Meghan chats with Cassandra Morales Thurswell, founder of Kitsch, about turning a passion project into one of the largest self-funded, woman-owned beauty brands in the U.S. From handmade hair ties to a global business, they dive into how grit, design, and a scrappy mindset fueled Cassie’s journey.</p><p><a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/bootstrapped-and-booming-with-kitschs-cassandra/id1803670198?i=1000709106177"><u>listen here</u></a></p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="e8007d60-1b09-40ae-b277-1234eb027c53" class="r-4a2a2j"><div data-rid="bf6ce3fa-a950-4fef-93b9-228b1aaa0c8b" class="r-1scuing"><picture data-rid="f7f5c513-d177-408d-8cf3-c1cd9aa28d0b" class="r-9rtaci"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/b2e010dd-7133-4065-8545-1d8f8db86d64?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/b2e010dd-7133-4065-8545-1d8f8db86d64?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/b2e010dd-7133-4065-8545-1d8f8db86d64?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/b2e010dd-7133-4065-8545-1d8f8db86d64" class="r-elywo0" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="e328a42e-1bf7-4571-a366-4fbfb12980a8" class="r-i3o4pp alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>EY National Entrepreneur of the Year 2025</p></span></div><div data-rid="64656fbc-b643-494f-84e6-94e9193ef4bd" class="r-1pj3pjt alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-d3101180-26d7-4941-8157-f0b0de59b8ca-attributes-textdecoration:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7328274409109053440">Cassandra Thurswell, founder and CEO of Kitsch, is honored as Ernst & Young’s 2025 Entrepreneur of the Year for her inspiring journey from crafting hair ties by hand to leading a globally recognized beauty brand. In this speech, she reflects on the grit, passion, and resilience that fueled her path as a self-made, woman-owned business leader.</a></p><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7328274409109053440"><u>watch here</u></a></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="2ab582e1-a2be-4664-9c8e-6adbe0dcc876" class="r-iza49f"><picture data-rid="508d99d0-4ece-4b18-bc79-084fa8e7f845" class="r-6j8ie8"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/5d2138a7-0f36-4f69-a996-bebd8c88fa1d?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/5d2138a7-0f36-4f69-a996-bebd8c88fa1d?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/5d2138a7-0f36-4f69-a996-bebd8c88fa1d?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/5d2138a7-0f36-4f69-a996-bebd8c88fa1d" alt="Two hair product boxes with pink ribbons on a pink background." class="r-o92gxy" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="1c3d9bfb-612d-4bfb-8360-a800360ec6b7" class="r-16gevor alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Behind Her Empire: EP 332</p></span></div><div data-rid="5b564924-6353-47bc-abb2-7fb5f806e111" class="r-1wgegxr alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-d3101180-26d7-4941-8157-f0b0de59b8ca-attributes-textdecoration:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><p>Cassandra Thurswell, founder of KITSCH, shares how she turned a handmade hair tie into a global beauty brand sold in over 27 countries—after seven failed ventures and years of hustling without outside funding. From couch-surfing and cold calls to fulfilling orders in her apartment, Cassandra reveals how trusting her gut and treating every job like a “mini MBA” shaped her 14-year journey to success.&nbsp;</p><p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=454Q1liJErs"><u>watch here</u></a></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="2195c61a-9dc5-4c94-8b6a-e5d53ca38c0f" class="r-1qnaye0"><picture data-rid="36de4a9d-01b9-4467-8537-56b224dd5df0" class="r-1hkd9wn"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/c3c7a52c-e825-406b-aa0a-8ddad8581429?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/c3c7a52c-e825-406b-aa0a-8ddad8581429?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/c3c7a52c-e825-406b-aa0a-8ddad8581429?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/ca52f6cc-83b0-47b8-94c4-4495ec17a7d1/c3c7a52c-e825-406b-aa0a-8ddad8581429" class="r-bn96y5" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="c828e4d5-6740-42a6-a375-8e7cc84fef34" class="r-1byfda5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Today Show</p></span></div><div data-rid="38d95a14-37c4-4de1-9b32-e949b051b55a" class="r-1tk1e8q alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-d3101180-26d7-4941-8157-f0b0de59b8ca-attributes-textdecoration:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><p>Entrepreneur Cassandra Thurswell, the founder and CEO behind the hair care brand Kitsch, opens up about the beginnings of her company and how she’s expanding into getting an entire aisle for her products at Ulta. Jill Martin shares her story.</p><p><a href="https://www.today.com/video/how-kitsch-founder-turned-a-passion-into-a-success-167054917945"><u>watch here</u></a></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="be71002b-667f-4613-a1bf-e760dd8672e8" class="r-jpytoi"><div data-rid="233d1ac2-39a1-4538-a648-982af0e888c0" class="r-y2ywt1"><div data-rid="be2a7afc-01d5-4d41-bbe7-3e2154c11046" class="r-1ouq9ac alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-62756da6-cf96-41b8-9068-07a5127bb6f6-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-2dc1ad1b-276a-4608-9168-ba60713a02ba-styles-e5ab0755-192d-43fb-99db-0f3b62468fef-attributes-textdecoration:undefined"><span style="width:100%"><h1>OUR STORY</h1></span></div><div data-rid="ccef48d8-60c7-43f8-a47a-563c91a227f8" class="r-qz6xz1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Kitsch started in 2010 with a simple idea: everyday beauty should be anything but ordinary. What began as a small collection of hair accessories has since grown into a global brand trusted by millions.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">We’re here to make your routine better—smarter, easier, more sustainable. From heatless styling tools to solid shampoo bars, every Kitsch product is designed to solve real problems with style and intention. No fluff. No overhype. Just products that actually work (and look great doing it).</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">As a self-funded, female-owned company, we’ve grown through grit, innovation, and a genuine connection with our community. And we’re just getting started.</span></p><p><br></p></span></div></div><picture data-rid="e00d255b-14cf-4e10-a019-b3878abd89e4" class="r-zwy23c"><source srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0104/6904/8384/files/TDAVIS_Kitsch_shampoo106_c6e7cff5-1f71-4dce-bc64-6c78be660b45.jpg